This repository includes data derived from the MAUD dataset (Merger Agreement
Understanding Dataset) by The Atticus Project, licensed under CC BY 4.0
(https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/).

  Source: https://www.atticusprojectai.org/maud

Specifically:
  - data/training/chunked/e0partial_sample.jsonl contains excerpts of
    merger-agreement text from MAUD.
  - The gold annotations under reports/*/gold*.jsonl and merged_gold.jsonl are
    derived from MAUD's labels.

Two upstream contracts (contract_88, contract_149) were corrected against their
EDGAR source filings before use.

